104
00:06:12.236 --> 00:06:14.736
Say, let's hurry and go eat some cake.

105
00:06:14.736 --> 00:06:16.636
I'm really hungry.

106
00:06:16.636 --> 00:06:18.236
All right.

107
00:06:18.236 --> 00:06:20.536
