108
00:06:20.536 --> 00:06:22.736
And as strong as you, Ran!

109
00:06:24.836 --> 00:06:28.836
If he fought with Makoto, I wonder who would be stronger at Karate?

110
00:06:28.836 --> 00:06:31.136
