112
00:06:32.936 --> 00:06:35.136
"Jeet Kune Do"

113
00:06:35.136 --> 00:06:36.836
Movie star Bruce Lee

114
00:06:36.836 --> 00:06:39.436
took the art of Kung Fu he had been practicing as a child.

115
00:06:39.436 --> 00:06:41.636
And combined it with boxing, judo, wrestling,

116
00:06:41.636 --> 00:06:44.936
savate, aikido and other forms of fighting

117
00:06:44.936 --> 00:06:46.436
to develop this martial art!

118
00:06:46.436 --> 00:06:49.136
But, it has a number of attacks that target vital points

119
00:06:49.136 --> 00:06:52.336
such as the eyes and throat, so it's pretty fierce.

120
00:06:52.336 --> 00:06:55.536
As usual, you know all kinds of weird things!

121
00:06:55.536 --> 00:06:59.636
Regardless, where are they having the cake buffet?

122
00:06:59.636 --> 00:07:03.336
We've come to a place where there's somehow nobody around.

123
00:07:03.336 --> 00:07:08.136
On the net, it says it's at the cafe on the second floor.

124
00:07:08.136 --> 00:07:11.236
Then, let's go to the second floor and take a look!

125
00:07:11.236 --> 00:07:13.436
There are elevators over there.

126
00:07:15.736 --> 00:07:18.236
Oh, where are you going, little boy?

127
00:07:18.236 --> 00:07:20.836
To the cake buffet on the second floor.

128
00:07:20.836 --> 00:07:23.936
Then, you can't get there using this elevator.

129
00:07:23.936 --> 00:07:26.136
This one goes to the annex.

130
00:07:26.136 --> 00:07:27.436
The annex?

131
00:07:27.436 --> 00:07:31.236
But didn't they say the annex was under renovation?

132
00:07:31.236 --> 00:07:33.236
Sorry for troubling you.

133
00:07:33.236 --> 00:07:34.536
No problem.

134
00:07:34.536 --> 00:07:37.736
We should help each other when in need!

135
00:07:40.536 --> 00:07:42.736
Mrs. Hirukawa!

136
00:07:42.736 --> 00:07:44.836
Sorry to have kept you waiting.

137
00:07:44.836 --> 00:07:47.136
How'd it go with him?

138
00:07:47.136 --> 00:07:51.136
At first he was drunk and shouting curses as usual, but...

139
00:07:51.136 --> 00:07:54.036
