140
00:07:54.036 --> 00:07:55.936
He cried?

141
00:07:55.936 --> 00:07:56.936
Yeah.

142
00:07:56.936 --> 00:07:58.336
He said that, after he had sobered up,

143
00:07:58.336 --> 00:08:00.236
he'd apologize to everyone and admit his sins,

144
00:08:00.236 --> 00:08:02.036
so he'd like us to go to his room.

145
00:08:02.036 --> 00:08:03.936
Really, now?

146
00:08:03.936 --> 00:08:07.136
But could he just be planning to spew nonsense

147
00:08:07.136 --> 00:08:08.936
to dodge our question?

148
00:08:08.936 --> 00:08:11.036
In order to get us off his back.

149
00:08:11.036 --> 00:08:14.436
Good point. He might say that

150
00:08:14.436 --> 00:08:16.636
he doesn't remember saying anything of the sort

151
00:08:16.636 --> 00:08:18.036
if we ask him about it later on.

152
00:08:18.036 --> 00:08:21.736
Then, why don't we record this repentance?

153
00:08:21.736 --> 00:08:25.636
That way, the other victims could hear it as well.

154
00:08:25.636 --> 00:08:29.736
But, I don't have any recording devices with me.

155
00:08:29.736 --> 00:08:31.136
Me neither.

156
00:08:31.136 --> 00:08:33.336
In that case, let's take my car

157
00:08:33.336 --> 00:08:35.436
and the three of us can buy one!

158
00:08:35.436 --> 00:08:39.536
Since he said it'd be a while before he sobered up.

159
00:08:39.536 --> 00:08:41.236
And we should be able to find

160
00:08:41.236 --> 00:08:43.836
