161
00:08:43.836 --> 00:08:45.136
You're right.

162
00:08:46.736 --> 00:08:50.636
No way! You're cutting off the line for the cake buffet?

163
00:08:50.636 --> 00:08:54.436
Yes. More customers than we'd expected came,

164
00:08:54.436 --> 00:08:55.736
"Cake Buffet Now Closed" -so there weren't enough cakes.

165
00:08:55.736 --> 00:08:57.436
If you're going to hold a cake buffet,

166
00:08:57.436 --> 00:08:59.936
you should prepare a whole lot and go out with a bang!

167
00:08:59.936 --> 00:09:01.536
A bang!

168
00:09:03.636 --> 00:09:05.336
What was that sound just now?

169
00:09:05.336 --> 00:09:07.136
Could be the parking lot?

170
00:09:15.536 --> 00:09:16.636
Hold on!

171
00:09:21.236 --> 00:09:23.136
This is bad.

172
00:09:23.136 --> 00:09:25.136
Call an ambulance!

173
00:09:31.536 --> 00:09:32.936
What just happened?

174
00:09:32.936 --> 00:09:35.836
We were just backing up the car

175
00:09:35.836 --> 00:09:38.336
when this man fell from above!

176
00:09:38.336 --> 00:09:39.936
Isn't this...

177
00:09:39.936 --> 00:09:41.436
Him?

178
00:09:41.436 --> 00:09:43.536
It is! It's Uesumi!

179
00:09:44.336 --> 00:09:46.536
What's the matter?

180
00:09:46.536 --> 00:09:48.836
Hold on, who's that over there?

181
00:09:48.836 --> 00:09:51.936
Someone suspicious was on the roof just now!

182
00:09:51.936 --> 00:09:52.936
What?

183
00:09:55.636 --> 00:09:57.836
Do you remember what that person looked like?

184
00:09:57.836 --> 00:09:59.836
I saw the clothes.

185
00:09:59.836 --> 00:10:03.036
It might have been an acquaintance.

186
00:10:03.036 --> 00:10:04.936
Ran, call the police

187
00:10:04.936 --> 00:10:06.936
and keep watch over this place with the security guard!

188
00:10:06.936 --> 00:10:09.336
-What? -I'm going with these people

189
00:10:09.336 --> 00:10:11.236
